		"description": "<h3 id=\"docs-internal-guid-80cd056b-7fff-3d32-774d-612c0492fc0b\" dir=\"ltr\">Advanced Armor</h3><p dir=\"ltr\"><em><strong>Prerequisite: </strong>Upgraded Armor</em></p><p dir=\"ltr\">You continue to upgrade your armor, which gains an option based on its type:</p><ul><li dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Advanced Light Armor</strong></li><li dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Advanced Medium Armor</strong></li><li dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Advanced Heavy Armor</strong></li></ul><h3 id=\"docs-internal-guid-47bef989-7fff-83ab-54f1-bdd3e8255fc2\" dir=\"ltr\">Advanced Weapon</h3><p dir=\"ltr\"><em><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Upgraded Weapon</em></p><p dir=\"ltr\">If your weapon does not have the Upgraded option for its type, it gains that now. If it does have that option, it instead gains the following one instead:</p><ul><li id=\"docs-internal-guid-80cd056b-7fff-3d32-774d-612c0492fc0b\" dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Advanced Weapon:</strong> Your weapon gains the <em>Vicious </em>property.</li></ul><h3 id=\"docs-internal-guid-db2fe54a-7fff-7ed3-22ea-cbd053a5510c\" dir=\"ltr\">Advanced Automaton</h3><p dir=\"ltr\"><em><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Upgraded Automaton</em></p><p dir=\"ltr\">You further upgrade your automaton. Its AC increases to 15, its hit points increase to 50, and you add one of the following options:</p><ul><li dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Antitoxin Module</strong></li><li dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Targeting Module</strong></li><li dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Flight Module</strong></li></ul>",
